long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Safebox is an extension for entering safe box passwords when providing personal multi-signature protection services for Ethereum on-chain assets.

The extension will help users to create a smart contract wallet in Ethereum and will allow them to set a safe box password, so that when using the safebox to store assets and then withdraw them from the safebox, they will need to enter your safebox password through the extension to complete the withdrawal operation. The user will be given details of the asset transfer in the extension's interface and will be able to perform sensitive operations such as entering a password in a secure environment, which the user can approve or deny

Safebox will only read the password entered by the user, and will erase the information about the user immediately after completing the asset transfer operation, without saving any information about the user or traces of the operation, it can be used like any other Chrome extension, at any time "View source code "Safebox", or on Github to view the source code.
